<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>{{subject}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .auction-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your Auction Has Ended!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    
    <p>Your auction for <strong>{{title}}</strong> has ended successfully!</p>
    
    <div class="auction-details">
      <h3>Auction Details:</h3>
      <p><strong>Winning Bid:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Winner:</strong> {{winner}}</p>
      <p><strong>End Time:</strong> {{formatDate endTime}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Next steps:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Contact the winner to arrange payment and shipping details</li>
      <li>Once payment is received, ship the item to the provided address</li>
      <li>Update the shipping information in your seller dashboard</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for using {{appName}}!</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p><a href="{{appUrl}}/support" style="color: #777; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Support</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
